<page breadcrumb=".." xmlns="http://gov.ns.ca/xmlns/page" xmlns:access="http://gov.ns.ca/xmlns/access-marker">
  <title>Amherst</title>
  <content>
    <html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
    	<h2>Access Nova Scotia Centre</h2>
		<dl>
			<dt>Address:</dt>
			<dd class="address"><access:address/></dd> 
			<dt>Directions:</dt>
			<dd>Turn right at Exit #4, continue past the Amherst Shopping Centre then past Kent Building Supplies, both on your right. RMV is on your right at the Superstore (directly across the street from the Cumberland Mall).</dd>
			<dt>Toll-Free:</dt>
			<dd><a href="tel:+1-800-670-4357">1-800-670-4357</a></dd>
			<dt>Hours:</dt>
			<dd class="hours"><access:hours/></dd>
			<dt>Note:</dt>
			<dd>Only Motor Vehicle Registration and Driver Licensing Services available after 4:30 p.m.</dd>
		</dl>
		
		<h3>Services</h3>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<h4>Business Licensing and Registration</h4>
				<h5>You can get application forms for the following licenses or permits:</h5>
 					<ul><li>Cemeteries and Funeral Homes 
 						</li><li>Debt Collectors and Consumer Reporting Agencies 
  						</li><li>Direct Sellers and Salespeople 
  						</li><li>Hearing Aid Dealers and Salespeople 
  						</li><li>Mortgage Brokers and Mortgage Lenders 
  						</li><li>Lenders Extending Credit</li></ul>
				<h5>You can get temporary (30-day) licences for the following: </h5>
 					<ul><li>Direct Sellers Salespersons 
  						</li><li>Individual Collectors 
  						</li><li>Cemetery and Funeral Services Salespersons</li></ul>
  				<dl>
					<dt>Hours:</dt>
					<dd>Monday to Friday - 8:30am to 4:30pm<br />(except holidays)</dd>
					<dt>Phone:</dt>
					<dd><a href="tel:+1-902-424-5200">(902) 424-5200</a> (Halifax area) <br /> <a href="tel:+1-800-670-4357">1-800-670-4357</a> (outside of Halifax area)</dd>
				</dl>
			</li>
			<li>
				<h4>Consumer Complaints and Information</h4>
 					<ul><li>Complaint Resolution 
   						</li><li>Education 
   						</li><li>Regulation</li></ul>
  				<dl>
					<dt>Hours:</dt>
					<dd>Monday to Friday - 8:30am to 4:30pm<br />(except holidays)</dd>
					<dt>Phone:</dt>
					<dd><a href="tel:+1-800-670-4357">1-800-670-4357</a></dd>
				</dl>
			</li>
			<li>
				<h4>Debtor Assistance</h4>
 					<ul><li>Consumer Proposals 
    				</li><li>Orderly Payment of Debts</li></ul>
  				<dl>
					<dt>Hours:</dt>
					<dd>Monday to Friday - 8:30am to 4:30pm<br />(except holidays)</dd>
					<dt>Phone:</dt>
					<dd><a href="tel:+1-800-670-4357">1-800-670-4357</a></dd>
				</dl>
			</li>
			<li>
				<h4>Registry of Joint Stock Companies</h4>
				<h5>The following services are available: </h5>
   					<ul><li>Search and Reserve a Business Name 
     				</li><li>Register Sole Proprietorship(s) and Partnership(s) </li></ul>
				<h5>You can also get information on the following: </h5>
  					<ul><li>Business Incorporation 
     				</li><li>Co-operative Incorporation 
     				</li><li>Society Incorporation (and Registration)</li></ul>
  				<dl>
					<dt>Hours:</dt>
					<dd>Monday to Friday - 8:30am to 4:30pm<br />(except holidays)</dd>
					<dt>Phone:</dt>
					<dd><a href="tel:+1-800-670-4357">1-800-670-4357</a></dd>
				</dl>
			</li>
			<li>
				<h4>Registry of Motor Vehicles</h4>
  					<ul><li> Driver's Licences 
      				</li><li>Driver Testing (By appointment only, please call the number below to book a time.) 
      				</li><li>Driver's Abstract (Record) 
      				</li><li>Vehicle Registration (Permits &amp; Plates) </li></ul>
  				<dl>
					<dt>Hours:</dt>
					<dd>Monday &amp; Tuesday - 8:30 a.m. to 4:30 p.m. 
						<br />Wednesday to Friday - 8:30 a.m. to 7:00 p.m.
						<br />(except holidays)</dd>
					<dt>Phone:</dt>
					<dd><a href="tel:+1-800-670-4357">1-800-670-4357</a></dd>
					<dt>Mailing Address:</dt>
					<dd>Registry of Motor Vehicles 
						<br />P.O. Box 1652 
						<br />Halifax, NS B3J 2Z3</dd>
				</dl>
			</li>
			<li>
				<h4>Residential Tenancies (Renting Residential Properties)</h4>
  					<ul><li>Information 
      				</li><li> Forms and Applications 
       				</li><li>Dispute Resolution and Hearings</li></ul>
  				<dl>
					<dt>Hours:</dt>
					<dd>Monday &amp; Tuesday - 8:30 a.m. to 4:30 p.m. 
						<br />Wednesday to Friday - 8:30 a.m. to 7:00 p.m.
						<br />(except holidays)</dd>
					<dt>Phone:</dt>
					<dd><a href="tel:+1-800-670-4357">1-800-670-4357</a></dd>
					<dt>Mailing Address:</dt>
					<dd>Registry of Motor Vehicles 
						<br />P.O. Box 1652 
						<br />Halifax, NS B3J 2Z3</dd>
				</dl>
			</li>
			<li>
				<h4>Vital Statistics</h4>
  				<dl>
  					<dt>Note:</dt>
  					<dd>This office accepts applications and payments; the documents you request are returned to you by mail. <br />
					Only the Vital Statistics Office, in Halifax issues documents at the counter.</dd>
					<dt>Hours:</dt>
					<dd>Monday to Friday - 8:30am to 4:30pm<br />(except holidays)</dd>
					<dt>Phone:</dt>
					<dd><a href="tel:+1-800-670-4357">1-800-670-4357</a></dd>
				</dl>
			</li>
		</ul>
