  					<dt>Note:</dt>
  					<dd>Provincial data can be found in the Halifax Land Registration Office.</dd>
					<dt>Hours:</dt>
					<dd>Monday to Friday - 8:30am to 4:30pm<br />(except holidays)</dd>
					<dt>Phone:</dt>
					<dd><a href="tel:+1-902-667-7231">(902) 667-7231</a></dd>
